@startuml seq_05_change_settings
title Sequence Diagram: UC-05 Change Settings

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "User Controller" as Controller
participant "User Service" as Service
participant "User Repository" as Repo

User -> Frontend: (1.1) Open Settings page
Frontend -> Controller: (1.2) GET /api/users/settings
Controller -> Service: (2.1) Load current account settings
Service -> Repo: (2.2) Find user settings by ID
Repo --> Service: (2.3) Current settings
Service --> Controller: (3.1) Current settings
Controller --> Frontend: (3.2) 200 OK (settings data)
Frontend --> User: (3.3) Display settings form

User -> Frontend: (4.1) Modify settings values
User -> Frontend: (5.1) Save changes
Frontend -> Controller: (5.2) PUT /api/users/settings {new_settings}
Controller -> Service: (6.1) Update settings request
Service -> Service: (6.2) Validate settings values
Service -> Repo: (7.1) Update settings in database
Repo --> Service: (7.2) Settings updated
Service --> Controller: (8.1) Updated settings
Controller --> Frontend: (8.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> User: (8.3) Show success message
@enduml
